org.vanilladb.core.util

Class Profiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vanilladb.core.util.Profiler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable

    public class Profiler
extends Object
implements Runnable
    A non-agent-based CPU profiler similar to 
     java -agentlib:hprof=cpu=samples ToBeProfiledClass
    but accepts filters and can be started/stopped at any time.
